title: Ebro In The Morning - Remembering Aaliyah + Yankees Streak
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/25.

Ebro and the crew discuss Andrew Cuomo's departure, the Yankees, and Busta Rhymes! Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (7, & 1:08), and you find out who played themselves. The crew remembers Aaliyah 20 years after her death (1:08).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
